						<div class="postbody">Hey all,
<br />
<br />To all my fellow yanks reading this, Happy 4th!  To everyone else, hi!
<br />
<br />Anyway, I seem to remember reading a post on here awhile back that I think was discussing instructions per second.  I can't find it now.  I'm just curious in finding out <em>roughly</em> (I know it changes depending on the opcodes) how many opcodes the 2A03 can handle during vblank after the NMI fires and during rendering time once vblank is done.  Does anyone know offhand?</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

